{
  "stem": "7546.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when my brother got bigger he helped out, and eventually I started working at the age of 14, when I finished public school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I graduated public school in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was interested in labor relations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a member of what they called the Bund, a socialist party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what they tried to do is sort of fashion themselves after the American labor movement.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, Poland was not a country where you could be freely a labor leader or be part of a labor movement.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when it came to a national Polish holiday he sometimes had to hide out, because they were afraid that the labor leaders or so-called labor leaders may speak out loud in public.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they tried to eliminate him, put him in jail for some reason or another for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember it, but I was told that my father was twice apprehended and put in jail until the national Polish holiday, which is the 3 of May, which equals the fourth of July here.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the holiday that the Polish government usually was very, very much afraid of.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One memory was that we had a neighbor, a Polish policeman, and he died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in Poland, a funeral became a public scene.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And usually the wealthier Polish people, when they had a funeral, they also hired a band.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I followed the band when he died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I followed the band and I was very, very much interested in that band.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why are they playing music?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was walking with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lo and behold, by the time I realized that I'm too far from home, I was in the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little did I know that at home, there was a panic already.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
